Form.Dispose(false) runs from Component.Finalize().  It must not detach owned
forms or clear Owner from that finalizer path: those operations mutate managed
Control collections and can call XplatUI.SetZOrder while the UI/backend state is
already tearing down.  Only the explicit Dispose(true) path should perform that
managed WinForms owner cleanup.

